'''
There are 4 major types of arguments:
    1 - Required argumements
    2 - Keyword arguments
    3 - Default arguments
    4 - Variable length arguments
Let's look at each one of them one at a time
'''

###1. Required arguments#####
#In this case the exact number of arguments are required to be passed in the order in which they are defined in the function.

def hello(name):
    print("hello", name)

hello("Duncan") #-> This will print 'hello, Duncan'